Name

xmpl - Shows off yuck.

Synopsis

xmpl [OPTION]... COMMANDdnl

Description

Shows off yuck.

COMMAND may be one of:

turbo
Run xmpl in turbo mode

-x, --extra-turbo Use more turbos than normal.

Recognized OPTIONs:

-h, --help
display this help and exit
-V, --version
output version information and exit
-x, --extra
Produce some extra bling.
-o, --output=FILE
Output bling to file.

Commands

xmpl turbo [OPTION]... [FILE]...
